{"tid":506544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泛民班人最仆街係成日畀假希望人。","createTime":"2017-12-22T10:09:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T07:56:15.000Z","uid":163916,"like":39,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e197deee08f888c04f8f789d465a85a78b8ee64e","tid":506544,"uid":163916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:09:45.000Z","msg":"永續快樂抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n修咗規就話要JR全委會法定人數廿人，又話DQ又乘。<br />\n<br />\n大佬，全委會同財委會都係委員會，你幾時見財委員有三十五人開會?<br />\n<br />\n當萬一俾你JR到廢佢一招又點? <br />\n<br />\n人地宜家有無限復會。中止，休會同縮短表決鐘聲又冇得再另作辯論。洗怕你?<br />\n<br />\n話要DQ人地40人就仲搞笑，對家揾咗個SC俾意見話無違反BL㗎，你點證明佢地蓄意藐視基本法呀? 俾個天阿法官造膽佢都唔敢啦。<br />\n<br />\n係唔係對家都夠票立廿三條同剪布啦，又唔總辭，楊岳橋班人真係議席大過天。<br />\n<br />\nDQ咗選返入去就算?<br />\n<br />\n大佬，垃圾會呢個遊戲Game Over咗㗎啦。<br />\n<br />\n鬼唔望條仆街餓死老婆瘟臭屋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外參加佢地初選仲要先畀八萬蚊民主黨班人，真係痴痴地線。"},{"pid":"bfa674dcc8cdce9d4b9531b8d6de9c5a9a869cb2","tid":506544,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:10:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa30e96b93150376e5b12f662bd778d818caa8f3","tid":506544,"uid":34223,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:12:14.000Z","msg":"泛民係神聖不可侵犯 你質疑佢地既話 你就係五毛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96c68ef458cd6ea20cacc612dcc78c4162297f84","tid":506544,"uid":47359,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:12:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我想反問返啲打手</span><br />\n<br />\n1.點解梁耀忠要讓個主席位畀保蝗梁君彥呀？<br />\n2.點解2011年泛民要支持修改議事規則削自己權呀？<br />\n3.點解馮檢基要走去新西票令何君堯當選呀？<br />\n4.泛民爭取真普選個時間表係點呀？<br />\n5.點解陳志全玩鐵鍊就當抗爭呀？<br />\n6.點解雨革要預約被捕而唔係同政府談判呀？<br />\n7.點解要玩篤灰割席呀?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同我答撚哂佢呀打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"792036f8112be98579d85335a643407c1b261cbe","tid":506544,"uid":47359,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:14:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">泛民打手邏輯<br />\n唔撐泛民就係五毛<br />\n<br />\n所以根據呢個邏輯青政民族黨都應該係五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"c6fd3bc56df536a8b8df362c890e612987a2ee99","tid":506544,"uid":51129,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:16:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">姐係樓主反對JR喇播？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08cfbfc5e0e5ea5f6c3a72a1ac4fded2ec8c564f","tid":506544,"uid":163916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:31:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">姐係樓主反對JR喇播？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n撐我就實撐，但係除左有得用法援出幾萬蚊糧畀泛民班大狀根本冇用。<br />\n<br />\n假希望，麻痹群眾。<br />\n<br />\n温水煮港豬。"},{"pid":"1c8f90cf32dfc30378a84730a75d8f46dd4ad290","tid":506544,"uid":39872,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:34:44.000Z","msg":"要加多句補充，首先保皇黨絕對要仆街冚家產"},{"pid":"17eb6bcd114600c8ebb0a4ae6d79ccb8770a8915","tid":506544,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:43:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">姐係樓主反對JR喇播？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n撐我就實撐，但係除左有得用法援出幾萬蚊糧畀泛民班大狀根本冇用。<br />\n<br />\n假希望，麻痹群眾。<br />\n<br />\n温水煮港豬。</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">姐係你撐一個唔單只冇用，仲會麻醉群眾嘅行動</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"497618d86db4e23db8c4f6bf69e343e8def58979","tid":506544,"uid":163916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:48:33.000Z","msg":"點解雙學三子入籠嗰陣佢地唔乘勢總辭呢?<br 